{"tid":787384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【特朗普細仔】無見一排變小巨人！ 12歲巴倫逾1.8米高","createTime":"2018-08-20T15:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T02:45:56.000Z","uid":29627,"like":199,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":111,"replies":[{"pid":"5b76aa8fc4dc9e223d7ddb2c8e55433525672a73","tid":787384,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T15:09:59.000Z","msg":"【特朗普細仔】無見一排變小巨人！ 12歲巴倫逾1.8米高<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180820/large/1534727692_c6d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180820%2Flarge%2F1534727692_c6d3.jpg&h=b54040af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統特朗普的小兒子巴倫（Barron Trump）年僅12歲，但看來身高已超越媽媽梅拉尼婭（Melania），直追爸爸了。<br />\n<br />\n暑假尾聲，巴倫周日跟父母一起由新澤西返回華盛頓，收拾心情準備新學年。<br />\n<br />\n去年開始入讀馬里蘭州私立學校聖安德魯主教學校的巴倫，今年升讀七年級。12歲的他，似乎遺傳了父母的「高大」基因，看上去已高過穿平底鞋的媽媽。<br />\n<br />\n根據Google資料，梅拉尼婭身高1.8米，換言之，巴倫已不只1.8米高，而且很有機會快將與高1.9米的爸爸「咁高咁大」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180820/58584484\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180820%2F58584484&d=51JnEPTXRju7sY6J5sQGeghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=968429ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180820%2F58584484&h=63e38754\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180820/58584484</a>"},{"pid":"56aaf21aaf626d1723b4ac6d00e47689dbcc1549","tid":787384,"uid":53837,"like":294,"dislike":1,"score":293,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T15:12:04.000Z","msg":"高咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8235540d0e9741db5eb3a61b6ce697b8a02f36e","tid":787384,"uid":94828,"like":311,"dislike":1,"score":310,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T15:20:07.000Z","msg":"好唔啱比例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj